name: jumping jacks
instructions: Jump and spread arms and legs, then return to the starting position

name: burpees
instructions: Squat, kick your feet back, do a push-up, jump back to a squat, and then jump up

name: plank
instructions: Hold a push-up position with your body straight

name: lunges
instructions: Step forward with one leg, bending both knees, and return to a standing position

name: bicycle crunches
instructions: Hang from a bar and pull your body up until your chin is above the bar

name: squats
instructions: Bend your knees and lower your body, then stand back up

name: mountian climbers
instructions: Start in a plank position and alternate bringing your knees to your chest

name: russian twists
instructions: Sit on the floor, lean back, and twist your torso to touch the floor on each side

name: high knees
instructions: Run in place, bringing your knees as high as possible with each step

name: box jumps
instructions: Jump onto a box or platform and then step down

name: dumbell rows
instructions: Bend at the waist and pull dumbbells toward your hips

name: leg raises
instructions: Lie on your back and raise your legs toward the ceiling, then lower them without touching the ground

name: jump rope
instructions: Jump over a rope, continuously swinging it over your head and under your feet
